snippet.title: Aquaman 2 Petition To Remove Amber Heard At Over A Million Signatures
snippet.description:
Aquaman 2 is already creating internet buzz with one of it's stars, Amber Heard, being the focus of an online petition. Fans of the superhero franchise (and her former spouse) have signed to recast the character of Mera. #Aquaman #AmberHeard #Entertainment
